title: Exploring Space - The Quest for Life
description:
The possibility of life beyond Earth is discussed by scientists. Included: computer-animated imagery; developments in astrobiology.

HD capture, DivX compressed, 720x404.

There was one video error and three audio errors in the 2 hour capture.  I had to demux the streams, add .5 secs of silence at a sceen changes close to 1:05:00 and then remux and fix the index to resynch the voices/lips of the last 50 minutes of the show.
